It allows you to host your software packages privately or publicly and use packages as dependencies in your projects. If GitHub experiences a service interruption to Packages, this could impact the dependencies you count on in your CircleCI builds. If this component is marked anything other than Operational, more information can be found at: https://www.githubstatus.com/

incident_updates.body:
We continue seeing this issue with the Bitbucket workflows due to the ongoing Bitbucket incident. 
Please refer to the Bitbucket status page: https://bitbucket.status.atlassian.com/incidents/rgwgpfyx0mpy
We are experiencing an issue where customer using Bitbucket may see failures for workflows that use contexts.
